snippet.title: Yuuma Game
snippet.description:
A silly little Touhou fangame where you play as Yuuma as she goes on a funny journey to recover her famous giant spoon, fighting many foes in a way only Yuuma can.

Available to download for free here: https://woah-maaan.itch.io/yuuma-game
